{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f7e9d6f78e","title":"给杨尚昆的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"460bd8b02f","index":0,"year":1953,"month":10,"day":22,"articleId":"f7e9d6f78e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"3f4d115fd3","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f7e9d6f78e","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央于1953年9月至10月召开的第二次全国组织工作会议。刘，指刘少奇。饶，指饶激石，当时任中共中央组织部部长。（4]胡养木，当时任中共中央宣传部副部长、毛泽东的秘书。总党委，指中央一级直属机关总党委。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b44f0f3dcc","type":"title","text":"给杨尚昆的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f7e9d6f78e"},{"id":"3f4d115fd3","type":"paragraph","text":"尚昆同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f7e9d6f78e"},{"id":"aaddb63ac9","type":"paragraph","text":"请将联共党史六条结束语印成单张，于今晚或明天发给到组织会议回的客同志，请他们利用停会的两三天时间，加以阅读、研究，可能时还加以讨论，使他们在刘少奇同志及别的同志在大会上讲话讲到这个问题时，已经有所了解。此事（印发结束语）在今日下午领导小组开会时，请告诉刘、饶及胡养木可同志一声。同时可多印一点（可印一二千份），发给北京的干部，并由总党委通知各部门、各党组要他们阅读和讨论","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f7e9d6f78e"},{"id":"f386f24399","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f7e9d6f78e"},{"id":"fec1d9cdb0","type":"paragraph","text":"十月廿二日二时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f7e9d6f78e"},{"id":"3bbace32a2","type":"paragraph","text":"H杨尚昆，当时任中共中央办公厅主任。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f7e9d6f78e"}],"page":{"id":"642248b672","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f7e9d6f78e","start":408,"end":408}}}},"__N_SSG":true}